divs: Sighting Detailsit was october 31 st, or november 1 st...around midnight.... i was coming home holloween night. i got home parked my car, got out(right by highway 94 and 694). and as i always do when i come home at night i scan the sky for a moment or so to see if any thing is cool out to see. as i was looking up i noticed this big black object...it was like 8 or 9 boomerang bird type shaped things all aligned in the shape of a stealth bomber but the weird thing was you could see the out line of a ship like object...it was not birds this for sure i know...it was really close to the ground and i didnt hear any thing or see whings flap...and the color of it was pitch black and no lights at all on it..the only reason i seen it was cuz it ccame into my field of vision as i was lookin up at the sky. it flew by and a medium pace as it flew over me it covered the sky where i looked. i have no clue what this was. it was gone with in 10 seconds of when i seen it...would any one have any clue what it might have been...?? maybe secret jet i donoo..
Summary: All black, no sound, no lights, similar to stealth bomber............
